---
// src/pages/index.astro
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Aditya Bhosale" />
  <title>Aditya Bhosale</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style is:global>
    :root {
    --bg: #ffffff;
    --ink: #1a1a1a;
    --ink-muted: #555555;
    --link: #1a1a1a;
    --rule: #d8d8d8;
    --cta-bg: #1a1a1a;
    --cta-bg-hover: #000000;
    --cta-fg: #ffffff;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
  }

  main {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  h1 a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .socials {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .socials a {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-right: 14px;
  }

  .socials a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--link);
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .label {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-top: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 17px;
  }

  /* CTA button — promoted current build link */
  .cta-wrap {
    margin: 36px 0 40px;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--cta-bg);
    color: var(--cta-fg);
    padding: 14px 22px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    background: var(--cta-bg-hover);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .cta-arrow {
    font-size: 0.9em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .cta-sublabel {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin: 36px 0 28px;
  }

  .footer-links {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-right: 18px;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* arrow superscript */
  .ext::after {
    content: " ↗︎";
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    body { padding: 40px 20px 60px; font-size: 18px; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; }
    .cta { font-size: 17px; padding: 13px 20px; }
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>

<h1><a href="/">Aditya Bhosale</a></h1>

<div class="socials">
  <a class="ext" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adityanbhosale" target="_blank" rel="noopener">li</a>
  <a class="ext" href="https://github.com/adityanbhosale" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gh</a>
  <a href="mailto:adityanb@sas.upenn.edu">email</a>
  <a href="/analyses">analyses</a>
</div>

<p>I'm an undergraduate at the University of Pennsylvania studying economics and computer science, minoring in biology. These days, I enjoy spending most of my time studying on-chain market infrastructure, prediction market design, and the bridge between regulated finance and public blockchains.</p>

<p>I'm an incoming 2027 summer M&amp;A analyst at Leerink Partners, a boutique investment bank in New York City, on the biopharma coverage team. Earlier work spans engineered T-Cell research at Penn's Center for Cell Immunotherapy, real-options pricing for clinical-stage assets at UCL's Global Business School for Health, and leading a handful of pro-bono tech / life-sciences consulting projects through Penn's Undergraduate Biotech Society &amp; Wharton's Venture Lab.</p>

<p class="label">some active interests</p>

<p>automated market makers, trading agents, scoring rules and information markets, tokenized real-world assets, regulated stablecoins, institutional-bridge thesis for crypto, biotech equity research, options pricing, market microstructure</p>

<p>Most of what I'm researching / building at the moment exists to close the gap between innovative DeFi systems (i.e. public blockchains) &amp; regulated capital markets. I think the most influential infrastructure in the next decade will be able to serve both, and the most interesting problems are the ones that require fluency in each.</p>

<div class="cta-wrap">
  <a class="cta" href="https://dual-layerbiotechliquidity.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    view current build
    <span class="cta-arrow">→</span>
  </a>
  <span class="cta-sublabel">dual-layer on-chain liquidity protocol — live testnet, full documentation</span>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="footer-links">
  <a class="ext" href="/cv.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cv</a>
</div>

</main>
</body>
</html>